0provide%20for%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2277c55fde-83b0-4eb2-8382-a2a641ee5814%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe're%20still%20stunned%20at%20how%20this%20all%20happened%20so%20fast%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20had%20windstorms%20in%20Altadena%20before.%20We%20went%20there%20at%209%3A30%20p.m.%20to%20batten%20down%20the%20hatches%20%E2%80%94%20put%20away%20outdoor%20umbrellas%20and%20check%20if%20furniture%20had%20blown%20over.%20We%20watered%20down%20the%20patio%20in%20case%20ashes%20or%20embers%20came%20in%20and%20disposed%20of%20a%20downed%20Christmas%20tree%20leftover%20from%20the%20holidays.%20We%20walked%20around%3B%20it%20was%20so%20peaceful.%20Then%2C%20we%20sat%20in%20the%20office%20for%20a%20minute%20to%20pray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20our%20mail%20and%20locked%20the%20door%2C%20giving%20one%20last%20look%20at%20our%20business%20before%20we%20got%20in%20the%20car.%20Although%20we%20saw%20the%20fire%20on%20the%20foothills%20near%20east%20Altadena%2C%20we%20never%20expected%20the%20winds%20to%20blow%20the%20fires%20so%20close%20to%20our%20business%2C%20let%20alone%20for%20it%20to%20catch%20fire.%20We%20didn't%20think%20to%20take%20anything%20from%20the%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2216cd1f90-3367-4542-ba73-56b02ecfc400%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20woke%20up%20scared%20the%20next%20morning%20and%20tried%20to%20check%20on%20our%20business%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20drove%20up%20at%206%3A30%20a.m.%20along%20West%20Altadena%2C%20thinking%20it%20would%20be%20the%20safest%20route.%20Everywhere%20we%20looked%2C%20houses%20were%20burning%20down%2C%20and%20businesses%20were%20on%20fire.%20We%20couldn't%20see%20through%20the%20pitch-black%20smoke%2C%20so%20we%20turned%20around.%20It%20was%20getting%20unsafe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20our%20daughter%20discovered%20online%20that%20the%20fire%20station%20half%20a%20block%20from%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20had%20caught%20on%20fire.%20When%20we%20heard%20that%2C%20we%20knew%20things%20wouldn't%20be%20good.%20Then%2C%20someone%20commented%20on%20one%20of%20our%20Instagram%20posts%20saying%20they%20saw%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20on%20fire.%20We%20tried%20to%20occupy%20ourselves%2C%20but%20we%20couldn't%20stop%20thinking%20about%20what%20might%20be%20happening%20to%20our%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20safe%20to%20return%2C%20we%20went%20back%20up.%20Nothing%20was%20left.%20We%20were%20stunned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Caf%C3%A9%20de%20Leche%20after%20being%20destroyed%20in%20the%20Palisades%20fire%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678820cde294a7514e8d5ad5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22564%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECaf%C3%A9%20de%20Leche%20was%20destroyed%20in%20the%20Palisades%20fire.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20courtesy%20of%20Matt%20and%20Anya%20Schodorf%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a9106625-c057-44a7-b6b9-980f85b47c4c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20realize%20our%20business%20is%20just%20a%20thing%2C%20but%20we%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20love%20into%20it%2C%20and%20it%20makes%20up%20the%20bulk%20of%20our%20livelihoods%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20a%20small%2C%20mom-and-pop-run%20business%3B%20we%20don't%20have%20investors%20or%20a%20franchise.%20We%20put%20everything%20into%20the%20business%2C%20and%20each%20d%C3%A9cor%20item%20was%20chosen%20and%20curated%20with%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20trying%20to%20find%20roles%20for%20the%20six%20permanent%20employees%20within%20our%20other%20locations%2C%20but%20in%20the%20meantime%2C%20we've%20set%20up%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fhelp-CDL-employees-after-the-eaton-fire%3Fattribution_id%3Dsl%3A59413510-aa83-459d-b291-a36e284d444b%26utm_campaign%3Dnatman_sharesheet_dash%26utm_medium%3Dcustomer%26utm_source%3Dcopy_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoFundMe%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20goal%20was%20to%20get%20%2410%2C000%20for%20our%20employees%2C%20and%20it%20was%20amazingly%20fully%20funded%20within%20the%20first%2024%20hours.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20over%20%2420%2C000%20has%20been%20raised.%20The%20support%20has%20been%20beyond%20anything%20we%20ever%20imagined%2C%20and%20we%20are%20grateful%20beyond%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20employees%20live%20within%2020%20minutes%20of%20the%20caf%C3%A9%2C%20if%20not%20directly%20in%20Altadena%20or%20Pasadena.%20Many%20had%20to%20evacuate%2C%20some%20lost%20their%20homes%2C%20and%20all%20have%20been%20impacted%20severely%20by%20this%20tragic%20event.%20We%20hope%20that%20these%20funds%20help%20bring%20them%20some%20comfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22183b7262-da88-489c-a257-65657572f5d0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20hope%20to%20rebuild%20and%20come%20back%20stronger%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20have%20special%20places%20they%20feel%20connected%20to%2C%20and%20this%20spot%20was%20that%20for%20many%20members%20of%20our%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20hope%20the%20insurance%20companies%20will%20be%20true%20to%20their%20word%20and%20cover%20our%20losses%2C%20and%20the%20government%20will%20pause%20payments%20on%20our%20mortgage.%20How%20can%20we%20pay%20a%20mortgage%20on%20land%20that%20no%20longer%20has%20a%20business%20on%20it%3F%20These%20are%20just%20some%20of%20the%20things%20we%20are%20worrying%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20those%20who've%20lost%20their%20homes%20are%20taken%20care%20of%2C%20we'd%20like%20to%20see%20some%20resources%20available%20to%20small%20businesses%20to%20help%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20hearts%20go%20out%20to%20those%20who%20lost%20their%20homes.%20We%20are%20very%20cognizant%20of%20people%20who%20lost%20more%20than%20we%20did%2C%20and%20we%20want%20to%20send%20love%20and%20support%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faltadena-cafe-destroyed-palisades-fire-community-support