27OV%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1.3%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20year%20prior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStahle%20said%20that%202025%20could%20mark%20an%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20inflection%20point%26quot%3B%20when%20demographic%20factors%20begin%20to%20lead%20to%20a%20decline%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffred.stlouisfed.org%2Fseries%2FCIVPART%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elabor%20force%20participation%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20he%20added%20has%20been%20roughly%20flat%20over%20the%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20that%20process%20starts%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20to%20reverse%20course%20without%20a%20massive%20surge%20in%20immigration%20or%20growth%20in%20labor%20market%20involvement%20from%20older%20workers%20above%20all-time%20highs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221dae0a24-b34d-46e3-90ed-7c090f5838e8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20gap%20in%20the%20workforce%20could%20be%20on%20the%20horizon%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%201.1%20million%20baby%20boomers%20retired%20in%202024%2C%20and%20an%20estimated%202%20million%20will%20do%20so%20this%20year%2C%20Adam%20Schickling%2C%20a%20senior%20economist%20at%20Vanguard%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchickling%20said%20there%20are%20roughly%208%20million%20working%20Americans%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2063%20and%2067%20%E2%80%94%20a%20common%20age%20range%20for%20retirement.%20While%20there%20were%20a%20similar%20number%20of%20people%20in%20this%20group%20last%20year%2C%20Schickling%20said%20a%20larger%20share%20of%20this%20year's%20cohort%20is%20older%20%E2%80%94%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2065%20and%2067%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20among%20the%20reasons%20Vanguard%20expects%20an%20uptick%20in%20retirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchickling%20added%20that%20some%20older%20workers%20postponed%20their%20retirements%20because%20the%20strong%20labor%20market%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20secure%20work.%20But%20he%20said%20many%20of%20these%20workers%20will%20likely%20choose%20to%20retire%20before%20they%20turn%2070.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B2025%20is%20shaping%20up%20to%20be%20one%20the%20biggest%20years%20for%20baby%20boomer%20retirements%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat%2C%20coupled%20with%20a%20smaller-than-usual%20cohort%20of%20people%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2020%20and%2024%2C%20suggests%20there%20will%20be%20a%20very%20low%20labor%20supply%20growth%20this%20year%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStahle%20said%20workers%20over%2055%20are%20spread%20across%20the%20labor%20market%20but%20are%20particularly%20common%20in%20business%2C%20management%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20education%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FLD4Ua%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Occupations%20with%20high%20shares%20of%20workers%20aged%2055%20and%20over%20in%202023%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221258%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Congressional%20Budget%20Office%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbo.gov%2Fpublication%2F59697%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprojected%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20that%20net%20immigration%20levels%20%E2%80%94%20and%20overall%20population%20growth%20%E2%80%94%20would%20begin%20declining%20in%202025.%20Additionally%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eon%20the%20campaign%20trail%2C%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20he%20would%20carry%20out%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjamie-dimon-policy-advice-donald-trump-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elargest%20domestic%20deportation%20in%20American%20history%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20the%20extent%20of%20his%20plans%20is%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20incoming%20administration%20follows%20through%20on%20promises%20of%20limiting%20immigration%20and%20implementing%20mass%20deportations%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20that%20we%20see%20the%20demographics%20impact%20the%20labor%20supply%20sooner%20rather%20than%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20Stahle%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeisure%20and%20hospitality%2C%20construction%2C%20and%20agriculture%20are%20the%20industries%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-mass-deportation-military-construction-agriculture-hospitality-national-emergency-visa-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehighest%20share%20of%20immigrant%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20are%20not%20US%20citizens%20as%20of%202022%2C%20per%20the%20most%20recent%20Census%20Bureau%20data%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20reached%20for%20comment%2C%20Karoline%20Leavitt%2C%20spokeswoman%20for%20the%20Trump-Vance%20transition%20team%2C%20said%20that%20as%20president%2C%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bwill%20enlist%20every%20federal%20power%20and%20coordinate%20with%20state%20authorities%20to%20institute%20the%20largest%20deportation%20operation%20of%20illegal%20criminals%2C%20drug%20dealers%2C%20and%20human%20traffickers%20in%20American%20history%20while%20simultaneously%20lowering%20costs%20for%20families%20and%20strengthening%20our%20workforce.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221059f30e-6de7-405d-9f41-314af7ab0f96%5C%22%3EA%20smaller%20workforce%20could%20ultimately%20hurt%20the%20economy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20it's%20uncertain%20how%20much%20retirements%20and%20changes%20to%20immigration%20levels%20will%20impact%20the%20US%20labor%20supply%20in%202025.%20Kory%20Kantenga%2C%20head%20of%20economics%2C%20Americas%2C%20at%20LinkedIn's%20Economic%20Graph%20Research%20Institute%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20retirement%20levels%20have%20been%20relatively%20stable%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20per%20LinkedIn%20data.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20specifics%20of%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20immigration%20policies%20haven't%20been%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20lower%20labor%20supply%20might%20help%20some%20Americans%20find%20work%2C%20it%20could%20also%20come%20with%20significant%20economic%20downsides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeclining%20labor%20supply%20can%20improve%20prospects%20for%20job-searchers%2C%20but%20too%20few%20workers%20can%20also%20result%20in%20inflationary%20wage%20growth%20and%20supply%20disruptions%20that%20perpetuate%20inflation%2C%26quot%3B%20Schickling%20said.%20For%20example%2C%20labor%20supply%20issues%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-deportation-immigration-policy-election-housing-home-prices-construction-costs-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econstruction%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20long%20relied%20on%20immigrant%20labor%20%E2%80%94%20could%20make%20it%20more%20difficult%20for%20the%20US%20to%20increase%20its%20housing%20supply%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKantenga%20said%20that%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehaving%20an%20economy%20with%20fewer%20workers%20could%20lead%20to%20lower%20consumer%20spending%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreat-labor-shortage-looming-population-decline-disaster-global-economy-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslower%20economic%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSlower%20growth%20means%20fewer%20opportunities%20for%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20it's%20not%20necessarily%20clear%20that%20it's%20going%20to%20make%20workers%20better%20off%20just%20because%20it%20may%20be%20easier%20for%20them%20to%20find%20a%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20looking%20for%20a%20job%20and%20comfortable%20sharing%20your%20story%20with%20a%20reporter%3F%20Please%20fill%20out%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScLu79elRbqrSr2cMp5JcqOQJheuCX77QuJqLYr9qEzH