EAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fif-my-car-not-safe-what-about-aam-aadmi-arvind-kejriwal-to-lieutenant-governor-1762704%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BIf%20My%20Car%20Not%20Safe%2C%20What%20About%20'%3Cem%3EAam%20Aadmi%3C%2Fem%3E'%3A%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Asks%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20can%20the%20common%20man%20expect...%20(when)%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20car%20is%20stolen%3F%20Law-and-order%20has%20been%20rapidly%20deteriorating...%20Police%20and%20law-and-order%20come%20directly%20under%20you%20(the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%2C%20controlled%20by%20the%20BJP).%20Please%20make%20the%20system%20robust%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20lamented%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20indicated%20in%20his%20affidavit%2C%20he%20has%20not%20personally%20owned%20a%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20declared%20income%20for%20the%20past%20five%20years%20ranges%20from%20a%20high%20of%20Rs%2044%2C90%2C640%2C%20or%20Rs%2044.9%20lakh%2C%20in%202020%2F21%20to%20a%20low%20of%20Rs%201%2C57%2C823%20in%202019%2F20.%20For%20FY2023%2F24%20he%20reported%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%207%2C21%2C530.%20His%20principal%20reported%20income%20source%20is%20the%20salary%20he%20receives%20as%20a%20Delhi%20MLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-assembly-elections-arvind-kejriwal-declares-assets-worth-rs-1-7-crore-owns-no-car-in-poll-affidavit-7483523%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKejriwal%20Declares%20Rs%201.7%20Crore%20In%20Assets%2C%20No%20Car%20In%20Poll%20Affidavit%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20AAP%20leader%20has%20said%20he%20has%20only%20Rs%2040%2C000%20in%20cash%20and%20had%20made%20no%20investments%2C%20but%20does%20have%20Rs%202%2C81%2C404%20in%20a%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20account.%20He%20also%20said%20he%20had%20no%20outstanding%20loan%20from%20banks%