billions%20worldwide.%20Yet%2C%20this%20dizzying%20success%20has%20come%20with%20its%20share%20of%20problems.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20the%20platform%20has%20become%20a%20lightning%20rod%20for%20controversy%2C%20with%20mounting%20concerns%20over%20data%20privacy%20and%20national%20security%20sparking%20fierce%20debates.%20Now%2C%20there%20is%20the%20very%20real%20prospect%20of%20a%20ban%2C%20which%2C%20once%20implemented%2C%20will%20have%20ripple%20effects%20across%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Data%20Threat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20first%2C%20let's%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20arguments%20and%20counterarguments%20for%20TikTok.%20The%20US%20government%20argues%20that%20Congress%20is%20acting%20on%20pressing%20national%20security%20concerns.%20They%20have%20painted%20TikTok%20as%20a%20wolf%20in%20sheep's%20clothing%2C%20claiming%20that%20ByteDance%2C%20its%20parent%20company%2C%20is%20a%20puppet%20of%20the%20Chinese%20government%2C%20ready%20to%20hand%20over%20reams%20of%20sensitive%20data%20at%20Beijing's%20command.%20They%20have%20called%20TikTok%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgrave%20threat%E2%80%9D%20to%20US%20national%20security%2C%20a%20digital%20Trojan%20horse%20smuggling%20Chinese%20influence%20into%20American%20smartphones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20claims%20are%20not%20backed%20by%20hard%20evidence%2C%20the%20fears%20are%20genuine.%20ByteDance%20operates%20under%20China's%20ominous%20national%20security%20laws%2C%20which%20compel%20organisations%20to%20cooperate%20with%20intelligence%20agencies.%20The%20logic%20is%20simple%3A%20data%20is%20power%2C%20and%20TikTok's%20ocean%20of%20user%20data%20could%20become%20a%20goldmine%20for%20China's%20global%20ambitions.%20Or%20at%20least%20that%20is%20what%20the%20US%20establishment's%20fear%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20TikTok%20isn't%20going%20down%20without%20a%20fight.%20Its%20defenders%2C%20alongside%20furious%20content%20creators%2C%20argue%20that%20the%20ban%20is%20an%20assault%20on%20the%20First%20Amendment.%20Shutting%20down%20the%20platform%2C%20they%20claim%2C%20stifles%20free%20speech%20and%20undermines%20the%20right%20of%20170%20million%20Americans%20to%20express%20themselves%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Change%20Of%20Heart%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20though%2C%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20the%20same%20man%20who%20tried%20to%20ban%20TikTok%20in%202020%2C%20has%20now%20become%20its%20unlikely%20saviour%2C%20albeit%20for%20the%20short%20term.%20The%20incoming%20president%20has%20urged%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20delay%20the%20ban.%20Why%3F%20Perhaps%20because%20he%20wants%20the%20glory%20of%20deciding%20TikTok's%20future%2C%20casting%20himself%20as%20the%20ultimate%20dealmaker.%20Forget%20Biden's%20administration%20or%20Congress%2C%20in%20Trump's%20world%2C%20only%20he%20can%20untangle%20the%20knot%20of%20national%20security%20and%20free%20speech%20wrapped%20around%20TikTok.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20two%20billionaires%20who%20have%20already%20met%20Trump%20have%20plans%20in%20motion%20to%20buy%20TikTok%2C%20which%20will%20be%20brokered%20by%20Trump%20after%20he%20assumes%20office%20on%20Monday%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20American%20tech%20history%2C%20the%20US%20has%20passed%20a%20law%20targeting%20a%20major%20Chinese%20tech%20giant.%20If%20the%20ban%20kicks%20in%20on%20Sunday%2C%20what%20lies%20ahead%20for%20the%20app%20and%20its%20millions%20of%20users%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHints%20From%20The%20Indian%20Ban%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20ban%20on%20TikTok%2C%20instituted%20in%202020%2C%20offers%20a%20glimpse%20and%20serves%20as%20a%20cautionary%20tale.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20app%20had%20amassed%20a%20staggering%20200%20million%20users%20in%20India%E2%80%94its%20largest%20global%20audience.%20TikTok%20was%20riding%20high%2C%20revolutionising%20digital%20content%20creation%20with%20an%20algorithm%20that%20empowered%20rural%20creators%20to%20achieve%20fame%20unimaginable%20on%20other%20platforms.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20content%20creation%20felt%20truly%20democratic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETikTok%20holds%20a%20similar%20cultural%20power%20in%20the%20US.%20%C2%A0Niche%20communities%20thrive%20on%20the%20platform%20and%20countless%20small%20creators%20and%20businesses%20depend%20on%20the%20app%20for%20visibility%20and%20even%20livelihood.%20But%2C%20just%20as%20in%20India%2C%20American%20users%20are%20already%20beginning%20to%20adapt%20to%20life%20without%20TikTok.%20Over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20as%20whispers%20of%20a%20ban%20grew%20louder%2C%20many%20creators%20adopted%20a%20fallback%20strategy%E2%80%94duplicating%20their%20efforts%20on%20rival%20platforms%20like%20Instagram%20Reels%20and%20YouTube%20Shorts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20migration%20has%20gained%20momentum.%20Recent%20reports%20reveal%20that%20droves%20of%20TikTok%20users%2C%20dubbing%20themselves%20%26quot%3BTikTok%20refugees%26quot%3B%2C%20have%20jumped%20ship%20to%20another%20Chinese%20app%2C%20RedNote.%20This%20week%2C%20RedNote%20surged%20to%20become%20the%20most%20downloaded%20app%20on%20Apple's%20US%20app%20Store.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20post-TikTok%20story%20suggests%20the%20void%20won't%20last%20long.%20Instagram%20and%20YouTube%20swiftly%20stepped%20in%20with%20Reels%20and%20Shorts%2C%20launched%20within%20months%20of%20the%20TikTok%20ban.%20Other%20startup%20platforms%20tried%20to%20compete%2C%20but%20they%20were%20no%20match%20for%20these%20entrenched%20tech%20titans.%20The%20same%20story%20could%20play%20out%20in%20the%20US%2C%20where%20existing%20giants%20are%20already%20positioning%20themselves%20to%20seize%20the%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TikTok%20ban%20could%20also%20be%20just%20the%20beginning.%20India%20didn't%20stop%20at%20TikTok%3B%20it%20axed%20hundreds%20of%20Chinese%20apps%20in%20one%20sweeping%20move.%20The%20new%20US%20law%20lays%20the%20groundwork%20for%20similar%20actions%2C%20setting%20a%20precedent%20to%20target%20other%20Chinese%20apps%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20national%20security%20and%20privacy%20concerns.%20The%20ripple%20effect%20could%20redraw%20the%20lines%20of%20global%20tech%20dominance%2C%20leaving%20Chinese%20tech%20firms%20locked%20out%20of%20Western%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Ban%20Could%20Be%20Devastating%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETikTok's%20revenue%20machine%20is%20formidable.%20In%202023%20alone%2C%20it%20pulled%20in%20%2416.1%20billion%20from%20advertising.%20The%20US%20has%20been%20a%20linchpin%20in%20this%20success%2C%20serving%20as%20one%20of%20its%20most%20lucrative%20markets.%20A%20ban%20would%20strike%20a%20devastating%20blow%2C%20slashing%20ad%20revenue%20and%20threatening%20ByteDance's%20global%20profitability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20with%201.6%20billion%20users%20worldwide%2C%20TikTok%20ranks%20as%20the%20fifth-largest%20tech%20platform%2C%20trailing%20only%20giants%20like%20Facebook%2C%20which%20boasts%20three%20billion%20users%20as%20of%202023.%20The%20app's%20dominance%20extends%20across%20Europe%2C%20Indonesia%20and%20Brazil%2C%20but%20a%20US%20ban%20could%20have%20cascading%20effects.%20Pressure%20might%20mount%20on%20Europe%20to%20follow%20suit%2C%20further%20jeopardising%20ByteDance's%20global%20growth%20trajectory%20and%20cementing%20the%20app's%20status%20as%20a%20geopolitical%20battleground%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Larger%20Anti-China%20Campaign%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20observe%20the%20US%20foreign%20policy%20closely%20would%20know%20that%20the%20US%20ban%20on%20TikTok%20is%20more%20than%20just%20a%20crackdown%20on%20a%20social%20media%20app%E2%80%94it's%20a%20calculated%20move%20in%20Washington's%20broader%20strategy%20to%20curb%20China's%20meteoric%20rise%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20global%20economic%20hierarchy.%20This%20pushback%20isn't%20about%20a%20single%20platform%3B%20it's%20a%20battle%20for%20technological%20and%20economic%20dominance%20in%20the%2021st%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETikTok%20isn't%20the%20first%20Chinese%20tech%20titan%20to%20face%20the%20heat.%20Huawei%2C%20once%20a%20juggernaut%20in%205G%20infrastructure%2C%20was%20hit%20hard%20by%20US-led%20sanctions%20and%20bans.%20As%20of%20January%202025%2C%20several%20countries%2C%20including%20Australia%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20Japan%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20EU%20countries%2C%20joined%20the%20US%20in%20restricting%20Huawei's%20operations%2C%20citing%20national%20security%20fears%20and%20allegations%20of%20espionage%20ties%20to%20Beijing.%20The%20message%20was%20clear%3A%20Chinese%20technology%20with%20potential%20links%20to%20the%20Communist%20Party%20would%20not%20be%20trusted%20in%20the%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHuawei%20Flashbacks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Huawei's%20revenue%20took%20a%20hit%20in%20international%20markets%2C%20the%20company%20rebounded%20strongly%20at%20home%2C%20leveraging%20its%20dominance%20in%20China%20to%20sustain%20operations.%20US%20sanctions%20curtailed%20Huawei's%20access%20to%20critical%20components%2C%20limiting%20its%20production%20of%20advanced%20smartphones%20and%20network%20gear.%20Yet%2C%20in%20a%20remarkable%20show%20of%20resilience%2C%20last%20year%20Huawei%20unveiled%20a%20cutting-edge%20smartphone%20powered%20by%207nm%20chips%E2%80%94a%20move%20that%20blindsided%20Washington%20and%20demonstrated%20the%20company's%20ability%20to%20innovate%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdapting%20to%20the%20global%20crackdown%2C%20Huawei%20diversified%20aggressively%2C%20pivoting%20to%20cloud%20services%2C%20IoT%2C%20and%20enterprise%20solutions.%20Despite%20the%20bruises%2C%20the%20company%20remains%20a%20formidable%20player%20in%20the%20tech%20world.%20The%20US-China%20standoff%20has%20evolved%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Btech%20war%26quot%3B%2C%20marking%20a%20new%20phase%20in%20their%20geopolitical%20rivalry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seeds%20of%20this%20conflict%20were%20sown%20during%20President%20Trump's%20first%20term%2C%20when%20a%20bruising%20trade%20war%20dominated%20headlines.%20Tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20imports%20soared%2C%20sanctions%20were%20slapped%20on%20Chinese%20firms%20and%20Beijing's%20economic%20momentum%20faltered.%20Trump's%20unrelenting%20economic%20offensive%20left%20scars%2C%20but%20it%20was%20under%20President%20Biden%20that%20Washington%20turned%20the%20trade%20war%20into%20an%20all-out%20technology%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20retained%20Trump-era%20tariffs%20totalling%20%24360%20billion%20and%20escalated%20the%20action%20further.%20He%20signed%20the%20legislation%20to%20ban%20TikTok%2C%20imposed%20sweeping%20export%20controls%20on%20advanced%20technologies%2C%20and%20restricted%20US%20investments%20in%20critical%20sectors%20tied%20to%20China's%20military%20ambitions.%20Tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20semiconductors%20and%20metals%20skyrocketed%2C%20while%20state-level%20measures%20barred%20public%20pension%20funds%20from%20investing%20in%20Chinese%20state-linked%20equities%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Ban%20May%20Have%20A%20Cascading%20Effect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20India%2C%20which%20faced%20no%20significant%20backlash%20after%20banning%20TikTok%20due%20to%20its%20negligible%20tech%20footprint%20in%20China%2C%20the%20US%20is%20deeply%20entwined%20with%20Chinese%20markets.%20A%20TikTok%20ban%20could%20ignite%20a%20new%20round%20of%20retaliatory%20measures%20from%20Beijing%2C%20threatening%20sectors%20far%20beyond%20technology.%20Trade%2C%20manufacturing%20and%20finance%20could%20all%20become%20collateral%20damages%20in%20this%20intensifying%20standoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20strategy%20to%20contain%20China%20goes%20back%20to%20Barack%20Obama's%20presidency%2C%20when%20Beijing's%20rapid%20economic%20ascent%20started%20to%20unsettle%20Washington.%20However%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20has%20arguably%20been%20the%20most%20aggressive%20yet%2C%20turning%20the%20US-China%20rivalry%20into%20a%20defining%20feature%20of%20global%20geopolitics.%20The%20TikTok%20ban%20is%20just%20the%20latest%20salvo%20in%20a%20broader%20campaign.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Syed%20Zubair%20Ahmed%20is%20a%20London-based%20senior%20Indian%20journalist%20with%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20Western%20media)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737013140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fboj4s1f8_tiktok_625x300_20_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhat-next-for-tiktok-if-us-really-bans-it-on-sunday-7485814%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20American%20tech%20history%2C%20the%20US%20has%20passed%20a%20law%20targeting%20a%20major%20Chinese%20tech%20giant.%20If%20the%20ban%20kicks%20in%20on%20Sunday%2C%20what%20lies%20ahead%20for%20the%20app%20and%20its%20millions%20of%20users%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhat-next-for-tiktok-if-us-really-bans-it-on-sunday-7485814%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Did%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan's%20Attacker%20Enter%20Building%3F%20What%20Cops%20Suspect%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENearly%2012%20hours%20after%20the%20life-threatening%20attack%20on%20actor%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20at%20his%20Bandra%20home%2C%20Mumbai%20police%20have%20identified%20a%20suspect%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%20The%20suspect%20entered%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20actor's%20home%20from%20the%20adjacent%20building%20after%20scaling%20the%20wall%20in%20between%2C%20sources%20in%20the%20crime%20branch%20said.%20The%20police%20also%20suspect%20that%20one%20of%20Mr%20Khan's%20house%20helps%20knew%20the