0quite%20similar%20to%20social%20networking%20sites%20like%20Facebook.%20It's%20based%20on%20principles%20like%20connecting%20to%20friends%20(or%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20LinkedIn%2C%20%26quot%3Bconnections%2C%26quot%3B)%2C%20posting%20updates%2C%20sharing%20and%20liking%20content%2C%20and%20messaging%20other%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinkedIn%20also%20puts%20a%20professional%20spin%20on%20ideas%20you%20know%20from%20Facebook.%20Your%20profile%2C%20for%20example%2C%20becomes%20a%20resume%2C%20complete%20with%20work%20experience%2C%20accomplishments%2C%20recommendations%2C%20and%20referrals%20from%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20site%20also%20offers%20things%20you%20won't%20find%20in%20other%20places%2C%20like%20a%20full-featured%20career%20board%2C%20where%20you%20can%20search%20for%20and%20apply%20for%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20employment%20services%20are%20now%20compatible%20with%20LinkedIn%20%E2%80%94%20when%20applying%20for%20a%20position%2C%20you%20may%20be%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-share-linkedin-profile%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshare%20your%20LinkedIn%20profile%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20sometimes%20means%20you%20won't%20need%20to%20painstakingly%20enter%20your%20work%20experience%20into%20a%20long%20online%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20new%20to%20LinkedIn%2C%20here's%20a%20quick%20tour%20around%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22237739e4-ed7e-4b32-ad89-f1b04826533d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20quick%20tour%20of%20LinkedIn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHome%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20akin%20to%20Facebook's%20news%20feed.%20Here%20you%20can%20see%20posts%20made%20by%20other%20LinkedIn%20users%2C%20and%20make%20your%20own%20posts%20that%20others%20can%20see%2C%20like%2C%20share%2C%20and%20comment%20on.%20Like%20Facebook%2C%20you%20can%20limit%20your%20posts%20to%20just%20connections%20in%20your%20network%2C%20or%20share%20your%20thoughts