upcycling%20more%20than%203%2C600%20kg%20of%20textile%20waste.%20These%20figures%20aren%E2%80%99t%20just%20numbers%2C%20they%20represent%20real%20change%2C%20opportunities%2C%20and%20hope%20for%20those%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EScaling%20up%20the%20mission%3A%20Threads4Good%E2%80%99s%20plans%20for%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2017-year-old%20initially%20funded%20the%20initiative%20using%20his%20personal%20savings%2C%20but%20he%20needed%20more%20funds%20to%20expand%20it.%20Currently%2C%20there%20are%20around%2026%20disabled%20individuals%20and%2013%20marginalised%20women%20working%20for%20the%20initiative.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20faced%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346172%2Fblind-german-woman-sabriye-tenberken-founded-kanthari-start-ngo-tibetan-script-braille-without-borders%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echallenge%20of%20fundraising%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20we%20needed%20money%20to%20pay%20the%20people%20who%20made%20the%20bags%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20solved%20this%20problem%20with%20grants%20and%20award%20money.%E2%80%9D%20Among%20the%20grants%20and%20awards%20that%20supported%20the%20project%20are%20the%20Diana%20Award%20(2024)%2C%20the%20Ashoka%20Seed%20Prize%20(Rs%2030%2C000)%2C%20the%20International%20Young%20Eco-Hero%20Award%20(USD%201%2C000)%2C%20and%20the%20Harvard%20Impact%20Initiative%20Award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20founder%20has%20ambitious%20plans%20for%20the%20future%2C%20including%20filing%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20(PIL)%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20government%20takes%20responsibility%20for%20ensuring%20proper%20attendance%20in%20government%20schools.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20the%20Right%20to%20Education%20Act%2C%20one%20of%20the%20key%20responsibilities%20of%20the%20government%20is%20to%20ensure%20proper%20attendance%20in%20schools%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20distribution%20of%20necessary%20stationery%20and%20facilities.%20Unfortunately%2C%20that%20is%20not%20being%20done.%20In%20the%20near%20future%2C%20we%20are%20striving%20to%20make%20sure%20these%20issues%20are%20addressed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20long%20run%2C%20we%20also%20want%20to%20introduce%20mid-day%20meals%20in%20government%20schools%2C%20so%20children%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20where%20their%20next%20meal%20will%20come%20from.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20hard%20work%20and%20dedication%20of%20Tejas%2C%20his%20volunteers%2C%20and%20the%20marginalised%20workers%2C%20Threads4Good%20has%20blossomed%20into%20a%20movement%20that%20not%20only%20addresses%20the%20issues%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F383933%2Fnarayanpur-high-school-environmental-education-sustainability-east-kolkata-wetlands%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducation%20and%20the%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20also%20creates%20a%20sense%20of%20dignity%20and%20independence%20for%20those%20who%20have%20been%20excluded%20from%20the%20mainstream%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20the%20journey%2C%20the%20teen%20founder%20humbly%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20amazing%20to%20see%20how%20something%20so%20small%20can%20make%20such%20a%20big%20impact.%20I%20am%20glad%20I%20decided%20to%20start%20the%20initiative%2C%20but%20I%20was%20overwhelmed%20when%20I%20saw%20it%20garner%20so%20much%20attention%20among%20students%20and%20their%20parents.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20learned%20that%20the%20power%20of%20community%20is%20unstoppable%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20excited%20to%20see%20where%20this%20journey%20will%20take%20us%20next.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Tejas%20Pugalia%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736911800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fup