5%2F01%2Ffarmstays-in-india-Nehamrit-Farms_11zon-1735895139.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D395032%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ajit%20Mishra%20transformed%20a%20denuded%2020-acre%20plot%20in%20Malshej%20Ghat%20into%20Nehamrit%20Farms%20%E2%80%94%20a%20thriving%20agrotourism%20destination%20featuring%20over%201%2C500%20fruit-bearing%20and%20indigenous%20trees.%20Supported%20by%20his%20family%2C%20the%20farm%20offers%20eco-friendly%20accommodations%2C%20organic%20farm-to-table%20dining%2C%20and%20interactive%20experiences%2C%20blending%20sustainability%20with%20rural%20charm.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F395032%2Fnehamrit-farms-malshej-ghat-maharashtra-organic-farmstay-balinese-tents-glamping-ajit-mishra%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Woman%20Is%20Connecting%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Floriculture%20Farmers%20to%20City%20Markets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmidst%20the%20lush%2C%20rolling%20hills%20of%20Mao%2C%20a%20little%20girl%20would%20hurry%20home%20from%20school%2C%20her%20footsteps%20quickening%20as%20the%20scent%20of%20fresh%20earth%20and%20wildflowers%20filled%20the%20air.%20Her%20parents%2C%20hardworking%20farmers%2C%20would%20be%20in%20the%20fields%3B%20she%20would%20eagerly%20lend%20a%20hand%2C%20carrying%20baskets%20of%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20from%20the%20farm%2C%20her%20small%20hands%20carrying%20whatever%20little%20weight%20they%20could.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20in%20the%20quiet%20corners%20of%20the%20land%2C%20where%20a%20patch%20of%20flowers%20bloomed%2C%20that%20she%20found%20the%20most%20comfort.%20There%2C%20tending%20to%20her%20lot%20with%20the%20same%20care%20her%20parents%20had%20taught%20her%2C%20she%20would%20look%20at%20their%20delicate%20beauty%2C%20unaware%20that%20these%20moments%20spent%20nurturing%20those%20flowers%20would%20t